  "english": [
    "<strong>MISHNA:</strong> What are examples of <b>vows that are unintentional</b> that are dissolved, as taught at the beginning of the chapter? One who vows: This loaf is forbidden to me as if it were an offering [<i>konam</i>] <b>if I ate or if I drank, and</b> then <b>he remembers that he ate or drank.</b> Or, one who vows: This loaf is <i>konam</i> for me if <b>I</b> will <b>eat or</b> if <b>I</b> will <b>drink, and he</b> then <b>forgets and eats or drinks.</b> Also, <b>one</b> who <b>said: Benefiting from me is <i>konam</i> for my wife because she stole my purse or she hit my son, and</b> then <b>it became known that she had not hit him or it became known that she had not stolen.</b>",
    "The mishna lists another example of an unintentional vow: <b>One</b> who <b>saw</b> people entering his courtyard and <b>eating figs, and</b> because he did not want them to do so <b>he said:</b> The figs are forbidden <b>to you</b> like <b>an offering. And</b> then <b>it was found</b> that <b>his father and brother</b> were in the group, <b>and there were others with them</b> as well, and certainly he did not intend to take a vow prohibiting his father and brother from eating the figs. In such a case, <b>Beit Shammai says: They,</b> his father and brother, <b>are permitted</b> to eat the figs, <b>and those</b> others <b>that were with them are prohibited</b> from doing so. <b>And Beit Hillel says:</b> Both <b>these and those are permitted</b> to eat the figs, as will be clarified in the Gemara.",
    "<strong>GEMARA:</strong> <b>The Sages taught: Just as vows that are unintentional are dissolved, so too, oaths that are unintentional are dissolved.</b> The Gemara asks: <b>What are the circumstances</b> of <b>unintentional oaths? For example,</b> as in the incident of <b>Rav Kahana and Rav Asi,</b> who disagreed about a <i>halakha</i>. During the dispute <b>this</b> one <b>said:</b> I take <b>an oath that Rav said</b> like <b>this</b> opinion that I hold. <b>And that</b> one <b>said:</b> I take <b>an oath that Rav said</b> like <b>this</b> opinion that I hold. This is an unintentional oath, <b>as each one took an oath properly in his own mind</b> and was sure that he was saying the truth.",
    "With regard to the mishna’s statement: <b>One</b> who <b>saw them eating,</b> the Gemara states that <b>we learned</b> in a mishna <b>there</b> (66a): If one vows to fast or not to eat a certain food, dissolution <b>is broached based on <i>Shabbatot</i> and based on Festivals,</b> since one certainly did not intend to include these days when taking the vow. <b>Initially, they used to say:</b> On <b>those days,</b> <i>Shabbatot</i> and Festivals, which he did not include in his vow, he is <b>permitted</b> to partake of the item, <b>and</b> on <b>all other days</b> he is <b>prohibited</b> from doing so. This was the case <b>until Rabbi Akiva came and taught: A vow that was partially dissolved is dissolved completely.</b> Therefore, one is permitted to partake on other days well.",
    "<b>Rabba said: Everyone</b> in the mishna, i.e., Beit Shammai and Beit Hillel, holds that <b>wherever</b> one <b>says: Had I known that</b> my <b>father</b> was <b>among you I would have said: All of you are prohibited</b> from eating figs <b>except for father, then</b> in that case <b>all are prohibited</b> from doing so <b>and his father</b> is <b>permitted</b> to do so. <b>They disagreed only</b> in an instance <b>where one said: Had I known that</b> my <b>father</b> was <b>among you then I would have said: So-and-so and so-and-so,</b> i.e., all the others, <b>are prohibited</b> from eating figs <b>and father is permitted</b> to do so."
  ],
  "gemara": [
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"0\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><big><strong>מַתְנִי׳</strong></big> נִדְרֵי שְׁגָגוֹת — ״אִם אָכַלְתִּי וְאִם",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שָׁתִיתִי״, וְנִזְכַּר שֶׁאָכַל וְשָׁתָה. ״שֶׁאֲנִי אוֹכֵל",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וְשֶׁאֲנִי שׁוֹתֶה״, וְשָׁכַח וְאָכַל וְשָׁתָה. אָמַר: ״קֻוֽנָּם",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אִשְׁתִּי נֶהֱנֵית לִי שֶׁגָּנְבָה אֶת כִּיסִי, וְשֶׁהִכְּתָה",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֶת בְּנִי״, וְנוֹדַע שֶׁלֹּא הִכַּתּוּ, וְנוֹדַע שֶׁלֹּא",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "גָּנְבָה. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"1\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>רָאָה אוֹתָן אוֹכְלִין תְּאֵנִים, וְאָמַר: ״הֲרֵי",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "עֲלֵיכֶם קׇרְבָּן״, וְנִמְצְאוּ אָבִיו וְאָחִיו וְהָיוּ עִמָּהֶן",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֲחֵרִים. בֵּית שַׁמַּאי אוֹמְרִים: הֵן מוּתָּרִים, וּמַה שֶּׁעִמָּהֶם —",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֲסוּרִים. וּבֵית הִלֵּל אוֹמְרִים: אֵלּוּ וָאֵלּוּ מוּתָּרִין. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"2\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><big><strong>גְּמָ׳</strong></big>",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "תָּנָא: כְּשֵׁם שֶׁנִּדְרֵי שְׁגָגוֹת מוּתָּרִין, כָּךְ",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שְׁבוּעוֹת שְׁגָגוֹת מוּתָּרוֹת. הֵיכִי דָּמֵי שְׁבוּעוֹת",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שְׁגָגוֹת? כְּגוֹן רַב כָּהֲנָא וְרַב אַסִּי, הָדֵין אָמַר:",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שְׁבוּעֲתָא דְּהָכִי אָמַר רַב, וְהָדֵין אָמַר: שְׁבוּעֲתָא",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "דְּהָכִי אָמַר רַב. דְּכֹל חַד וְחַד אַדַּעְתָּא דְנַפְשֵׁיהּ",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שַׁפִּיר קָמִישְׁתְּבַע. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"3\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>רָאָה אוֹתָן אוֹכְלִין.",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "תְּנַן הָתָם: פּוֹתְחִין בְּשַׁבָּתוֹת וּבְיָמִים טוֹבִים. בָּרִאשׁוֹנָה",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הָיוּ אוֹמְרִים: אוֹתָן הַיָּמִים — מוּתָּרִים, וּשְׁאָר",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "כׇּל הַיָּמִים — אֲסוּרִים, עַד שֶׁבָּא רַבִּי עֲקִיבָא",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וְלִימֵּד: נֶדֶר שֶׁהוּתַּר מִקְצָתוֹ הוּתַּר כֻּלּוֹ.",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"4\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אָמַר רַבָּה: דְּכוּלֵּי עָלְמָא, כֹּל הֵיכָא דְּאָמַר:",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אִילּוּ הָיִיתִי יוֹדֵעַ שֶׁאַבָּא בֵּינֵיכֶם, הָיִיתִי אוֹמֵר",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "״כּוּלְּכֶם אֲסוּרִין חוּץ מֵאַבָּא״, דְּכוּלְּהוֹן אֲסוּרִין",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וְאָבִיו מוּתָּר. לֹא נֶחְלְקוּ אֶלָּא בְּאוֹמֵר:",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אִילּוּ הָיִיתִי יוֹדֵעַ שֶׁאַבָּא בֵּינֵיכֶם, הָיִיתִי",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אוֹמֵר: ״פְּלוֹנִי וּפְלוֹנִי אֲסוּרִין וְאַבָּא מוּתָּר״.",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    }
  ],
  "rashi": [
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>מַתְנִי׳ נִדְרֵי שְׁגָגוֹת.</b> אמר קונם כו': <b>ונזכר</b> <b>שאכל</b> <b>ושתה.</b> פטור",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 25b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דלבו אונסו דסבר שבאמת נשבע: <b>וכן</b> <b>ראה</b> <b>אותם</b> <b>אוכלים</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 25b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>תאנים</b> <b>ואמר</b> <b>הרי</b> <b>הן</b> <b>עליכם</b> <b>קרבן</b> <b>ונמצאו.</b> אותן האוכלים שהיה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 25b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "אביו או אחיו היינו נמי נדרי שגגות שאילו היה יודע שהיה אביו או",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 25b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "אחיו לא היה מדירן: <b>או</b> <b>שהיה</b> <b>אוכל</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 25b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>עמהן.</b> עם אביו ועם אחיו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 25b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "אחרים: <b>בש\"א</b> <b>הן</b> <b>מותרין.</b> אביו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 25b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ואחיו בלבד ומה שעמהם אסורים",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 25b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דקסברי נדר שהותר מקצתו לא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 25b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "הותר כולו וב\"ה סברי נדר שהותר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 25b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "מקצתו הותר כולו. ע\"כ מפי' רבינו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 25b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "גרשום זצ\"ל: <b>גמ'</b> <b>תנן</b> <b>התם.</b> בפרק",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 25b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ר\"א אומר כו': <b>פותחין</b> <b>בשבתות</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 25b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>וימים</b> <b>טובים.</b> שאם נדר שלא יאכל",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 25b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "כל ימות השנה פותחין לו חרטה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 25b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "כך כלום נדרת על דעת להתענות",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 25b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "בשבתות וימים טובים אם יאמר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 25b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "לאו: <b>בראשונה.</b> היו ב\"ד של",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 25b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ראשונים אומרים אותן הימים שבתות",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 25b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "וי\"ט מותרין וכו': <b>הותר</b> <b>כולו.</b> וכולן",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 25b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "מותרין: <b>אמר</b> <b>רבה</b> <b>הכל</b> <b>מודים</b> <b>כו'.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 25b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "אמתני' קאי כלומר שאם ראה אותם",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 25b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "אוכלים תאנים וענבים ואמר הרי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 25b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "הן עליכם קרבן (כמו שאמר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 25b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "עליהם על כולכם אסורין) ושוב",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 25b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "אמר אילו הייתי יודע שאבא ביניכם",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nedarim 25b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "הייתי אומר כולכם אסורים חוץ",
